Set the controller type to PS4:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='PS4' -o PH_CTRL_MAP='no'
Set the controller type to PS4 with XBOX360 controller emulation:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='PS4' -o PH_CTRL_MAP='yes'
View help on how to configure a usb PS4 controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c usb -t PS4
View help on how to configure a PS4 controller using the Sony Wireless Adapter:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c sonywadapt -t PS4
View help on how to configure a bluetooth PS4 controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c bluetooth -t PS4
Interactively configure bluetooth PS4 controller(s):confctrl_ph.sh -p prompt -t PS4
XBOX360 controllers menu:ph_show_menu XBOX360
PS3 controllers menu:ph_show_menu PS3
AppManagement menu:ph_show_menu AppManagement
Apps menu:ph_show_menu Apps
Controllers menu:ph_show_menu Controllers
Advanced menu:ph_show_menu Advanced
Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
